<plot>Sixty Days is a story about the interconnected lives of four city dwellers: the wealthy James, the schizophrenic Michelle, a nameless troubled retail clerk and Corrine, a jaded but beautiful street prostitute living under a cloud of drugs and abuse. Alienated from the world and strangely connected through random social gatherings, the four misfits disregard both each other and themselves as they struggle to find meaning without getting swallowed by the impartial city.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?499651</url></doc>
